## Resolved Type Decisions
1. StoreRepr::Positional(Arc<PositionalStore>) — Arc enables O(1) snapshot via refcount clone
2. indexes() -> Option<&Indexes> — None for Positional (no Indexes exist). Tests .unwrap()
3. from_merge(Pos, OrdMap) builds temp PositionalStore from OrdSet — cannot promote() on &Store
4. live_causal/live_set built from positional.datoms().iter() — no OrdSet in constructor
5. DatomIter: Iterator + ExactSizeIterator, delegates size_hint to backing iterator
6. DatomSetView::PartialEq via iter().eq() — both variants EAVT-sorted
7. Snapshot::datoms() returns DatomIter dispatching on SnapshotDatoms variant

