- **Abstract** (spec says): INV-FERR-020 transaction atomicity — typestate enforces single-use. Ownership transfer prevents double-application.
- **Concrete** (code must): Add into_datoms(self) consuming method. Reorder apply.rs to read agent() before consuming. Remove .to_vec() in db/transact.rs — receipt.datoms() borrow suffices.
- **Coupling** (verified by): Zero `.to_vec()` calls on transaction datoms or receipt datoms in the transact path. Compile error on calling `transaction.agent()` after `transaction.into_datoms()`.

